With the exception below, the Basement project is distributed under the terms
of the MIT license (see LICENSE).

The Basement project also bundles patch files, which are applied to the sources
of the various packages. Those patches are not covered by the license of the
Basement project. Instead, they are covered by the license of the software to
which the patches are applied. When said software is available under multiple
licenses, the Basement patches are only provided under the publicly accessible
licenses.
